text: Nabii Ibraahimih Iscaaqh deqsita baxaa kee Iscaaqh baxa Yaq- qhuub kaah necee, ken nammayak kulli num tirri hayneeh keenik dumaak Nabii Nuuc cakkî fanah tirri hayne, Nabii Nuuc samadak Nabii Daawuuduuy Nabii Suleymaanaay, Nabii Ayyuub kee Nabii Yuusufuuy, Nabii Muusaa kee Nabii Haaruun inkih cakkî fanah tirri ken hayne, tama Ambiya abiten maqaanel ken kah galatne innaah, meqem abite mara tamannal galatna
